- **Tavus API Documentation**: [dev_docs/tavus.txt](mdc:dev_docs/tavus.txt) - Complete Tavus CVI documentation including function calling, personas, and layers
- **Product Requirements**: [dev_docs/PRD.md](mdc:dev_docs/PRD.md) - Rosa project specifications for CTBTO SnT 2025 conference

