  - [examples/cvi-hover-over-website/](mdc:examples/cvi-hover-over-website) - Click interaction tools
  - [examples/cvi-custom-llm-with-backend/](mdc:examples/cvi-custom-llm-with-backend) - Custom LLM integration

## Rosa Project Context
- Building a multilingual (6 UN languages) diplomatic conference assistant
- Requires function calling for Python backend integration
- Split-screen UI: avatar + dynamic content (QR codes, maps, bios)
- Strict "red zone" filtering and <200ms response times
- Touchless, voice-only interaction for kiosk deployment

## Architecture
- **Frontend**: React + Tavus CVI UI components + Daily.co
- **Backend**: Python multi-agent system accessible via function calls
- **Integration**: Tavus function calling bridges React UI to Python logic
